{"tid":239782,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"摩連奴：歐霸盃冠軍毫無意義","createTime":"2017-05-12T01:46:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-16T06:08:38.000Z","uid":19552,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5cf6d81555abcd5dbb675c06895cbec7a669a432","tid":239782,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T01:46:48.000Z","msg":"車路士領隊摩連奴表示，對於「藍戰士」這種級別的球隊來說，贏下歐霸盃冠軍根本算不上是一件好事。<br />\n<br />\n賓尼迪斯在2012-13球季曾率領車路士取得了球會歷史上首座的歐霸盃冠軍，不過摩帥卻認為這個獎盃毫無意義。<br />\n<br />\n在BT Sport製作的一部摩連奴的紀錄片中，該名葡萄牙教頭如此說：「當我回到車路士的時候，我感覺到球隊參加歐霸盃的經歷是毫無益處的。」<br />\n<br />\n「歐霸盃根本沒辦法和歐聯相比。無論是這項賽事的水準、參賽的球員、球隊和歐聯都不是一個等級的。一家大球會參加和贏得歐霸盃冠軍是毫無益處的一件事。」"},{"pid":"04d9f4f85e982bb3767ea7a9893818112de153db","tid":239782,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T01:48:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8149a9a558b0475d17e80d3a4322e447acf7638d","tid":239782,"uid":22589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T01:49:11.000Z","msg":"拎完係你地面前踩"},{"pid":"d5028855d1c988641c9ad56770b5cc1a5f47c297","tid":239782,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T05:34:17.000Z","msg":"4年前你好愛你女朋友<br />\n而家呢？"},{"pid":"3140eb4acb6a1de235a1f57e8fff3f6c1e4de582","tid":239782,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T05:34:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>4年前你好愛你女朋友<br />\n而家呢？</blockquote><br />\n未出世"},{"pid":"6cd2d698ed28680e205b561dc9c78b485a9f683b","tid":239782,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T05:37:01.000Z","msg":"唔小心入左決賽，sor9"},{"pid":"28cd6e6a952b7741ad91f5a2d4ab85b0905481f1","tid":239782,"uid":9548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T05:38:31.000Z","msg":"宜家贏冠軍有歐聯打，點同<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3862a42ed4e075e380f5a44eb4676833e826709a","tid":239782,"uid":1790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T05:39:29.000Z","msg":"<bloc